OL,7,FThe changes included protecting people
OL,8,Fclaiming personal independence payment
OL,9,F(Pip) from changes due to come into
OL,10,Feffect in November 2026, and rowing
OL,11,Fback plans to cut the health-related
OL,12,Felement of universal credit.
OL,14,FOne of the other key concessions
OL,15,Foffered to angry backbenchers was that
OL,16,Fa review into the Pip process will be
OL,17,F'co-produced' with disabled people.
