OL,7,FThe biggest rebellion Starmer has
OL,8,Ffaced previously was when 16 Labour
OL,9,FMPs voted against the government
OL,10,Fduring the passage of the Planning and
OL,11,FInfrastructure Bill.
OL,13,F52 Labour MPs abstained when the
OL,14,Fgovernment cut the winter fuel
OL,15,Fallowance for millions of pensioners
OL,16,Flast year, while only one MP voted
OL,17,Fagainst the plans, which have now been
OL,18,Fpartially reversed after the
OL,19,Fgovernment u-turned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
