OL,7,FThe largest rebellion in the first
OL,8,Fyear of the last Labour government
OL,9,Funder Tony Blair was 47 over the Lone
OL,10,FParent Benefit, while the biggest
OL,11,Frevolt in Blair's first Parliament was
OL,12,Falso over incapacity benefit as 67 MPs
OL,13,Fvoted against the government.
OL,15,FThe vote on Tuesday was on the
OL,16,Foriginal wording of the bill before
OL,17,Fthe concessions, but the government
OL,18,Fhave confirmed they will table an
OL,19,Famendment after the vote before the
OL,20,FBill reaches the next stage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
